title: Microsoft Office 2003 Professional with Business Contact Manager
description:
Ripped from a 3-disc set, Gateway OEM (from the COA on the back cover). Microsoft Part Number X11-12332. Product key not included.

System Requirements:

- 233 MHz Pentium Processor
- 128 MB of RAM
- 400 MB of hard disk space
- Super VGA with 800 x 600 resolution and 256 colors
- CD-ROM drive

Outlook 2003 with Business Contact Manager:

- 450 MHz Pentium III Processor
- 256 MB of RAM
- 190 MB of hard disk space

InfoPath:

- Internet Explorer 6 or later

* You cannot use the Business Contact Manager add-in for Outlook 2003 with Microsoft Exchange Server
